title: 2017 Week 3 Preview and Chris Wesseling's Return
itunes:title: 2017 Week 3 Preview and Chris Wesseling's Return
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal are finally all back together to discuss the Week 3 preview and the exciting Thursday night spectacle between the Rams and the 49ers.
